{"id":207,"parent_id":193,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":207,"title":"Joshua 14","subtitle":"","short_title":"Josh.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 14"],[".studySummary",["i","The land is divided by lot among 9½ tribes—Caleb inherits Hebron as a special reward for his faithfulness."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.1","order":"02.07.014.18417"},["b","1"],"And these",["i","are the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"countries"]],"which the children of Israel inherited in the land of Canaan, which Eleazar the priest, and Joshua the son of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Nun"],", and the heads of the fathers of the tribes of the children of Israel, distributed for inheritance to them."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.2","order":"02.07.014.18418"},["b","2"],"By",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"lot"],["i","was"],"their inheritance, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded by the hand of Moses, for the nine tribes, and",["i","for"],"the half tribe."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.3","order":"02.07.014.18419"},["b","3"],"For Moses had given the inheritance of two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"tribes"],"and an half tribe on the other side Jordan: but unto the Levites he gave none inheritance among them."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.4","order":"02.07.014.18420"},["b","4"],"For the children of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Joseph"],"were two tribes, Manasseh and Ephraim: therefore they gave no part unto the Levites in the land, save cities to dwell",["i","in,"],"with their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"suburbs"],"for their cattle and for their substance."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.5","order":"02.07.014.18421"},["b","5"],"As the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded Moses, so the children of Israel did, and they divided the land."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.6","order":"02.07.014.18422"},["b","6"],"¶Then the children of Judah came unto Joshua in Gilgal: and Caleb the son of Jephunneh the Kenezite said unto him, Thou knowest the thing that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses the man of God concerning me and thee in Kadesh-barnea."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.7","order":"02.07.014.18423"},["b","7"],"Forty years old",["i","was"],"I when Moses the servant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"sent"],"me from Kadesh-barnea to espy out the land; and I brought him word again as",["i","it was"],"in mine heart."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.8","order":"02.07.014.18424"},["b","8"],"Nevertheless my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"brethren"],"that went up with me made the heart of the people melt: but I wholly",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"followed"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.9","order":"02.07.014.18425"},["b","9"],"And Moses sware on that day, saying, Surely the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"land"],"whereon thy feet have trodden shall be thine inheritance, and thy children’s for ever, because thou hast wholly followed the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.10","order":"02.07.014.18426"},["b","10"],"And now, behold, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath kept me alive,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"as"],"he said, these forty and five years, even since the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake this word unto Moses, while",["i","the children of"],"Israel wandered in the wilderness: and now, lo, I",["i","am"],"this day fourscore and five years old."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.11","order":"02.07.014.18427"},["b","11"],"As yet I",["i","am as"],"strong this day as",["i","I was"],"in the day that Moses sent me: as my strength",["i","was"],"then, even so",["i","is"],"my strength now, for war, both to go out, and to come in."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.12","order":"02.07.014.18428"},["b","12"],"Now therefore give me this mountain, whereof the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake in that day; for thou heardest in that day how the Anakims",["i","were"],"there, and",["i","that"],"the cities",["i","were"],"great",["i","and"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"fenced"],": if so be the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","will be"],"with me, then I shall be able to drive them out, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.13","order":"02.07.014.18429"},["b","13"],"And Joshua blessed him, and gave unto Caleb the son of Jephunneh Hebron for an inheritance."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.14","order":"02.07.014.18430"},["b","14"],"Hebron therefore became the inheritance of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Caleb"],"the son of Jephunneh the Kenezite unto this day, because that he wholly followed the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.15","order":"02.07.014.18431"},["b","15"],"And the name of Hebron before",["i","was"],"Kirjath-arba;",["i","which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Arba"],"was"],"a great man among the Anakims. And the land had rest from war."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.1a","order":"02.07.014.18432"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/34.17"},"Num. 34:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.1b","order":"02.07.014.18434"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.28"},"Num. 11:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18"},"27:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.2a","order":"02.07.014.18436"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/18.6"},"Josh. 18:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/102.34"},"D&C 102:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.3a","order":"02.07.014.18438"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/13.8.7-8"},"Josh. 13:8 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.4a","order":"02.07.014.18440"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/5.1.1-2"},"1 Chr. 5:1 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/47.13"},"Ezek. 47:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.4b","order":"02.07.014.18442"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/35.2.2-5"},"Num. 35:2 (2–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.7a","order":"02.07.014.18444"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/13.2.2-3,6"},"Num. 13:2 (2–3, 6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.8a","order":"02.07.014.18446"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/13.31.30-33"},"Num. 13:31 (30–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.8b","order":"02.07.014.18448"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/14.24"},"Num. 14:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.9a","order":"02.07.014.18450"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/13.22"},"Num. 13:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.10a","order":"02.07.014.18452"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/14.24"},"Num. 14:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.12a","order":"02.07.014.18454"},["b","12a"],["span.small","OR"],"fortified."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.14a","order":"02.07.014.18456"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/21.12"},"Josh. 21:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.15a","order":"02.07.014.18458"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/21.11"},"Josh. 21:11"],"."]]}
